<li>For more infomation
Markdown is available at <a href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/">http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/</a>
and <a href="http://wenku.baidu.com/view/5e737dec102de2bd96058843.html">there is a simple markdown syntax in the wenku.baidu.com</a></li>
</ol>


<h2>Preview your blog in local</h2>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
